---
import { SkeletonPage, BasicPage } from '@layouts'
import { SEO } from '@components'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'

const lang = { code: 'fr' }
---

<SkeletonPage {lang}>
  <SEO
    slot="head"
    ogType="website"
    title="Inauguration Wanna Play - 10 juin 2018"
    description="Retour sur l'événement fondateur de Wanna Play : l'invocation de Ruego."
    socialImage={'/archive/images/mailChimp_header-invitation-2.png'}
    ogVideo={false}
    twitterCard="summary"
  />

  <BasicPage {lang}>
    <main class="center max" style="margin-top: 0;">
      <header class="flow gap-h4 center text">
        <Image
          src="/archive/images/mailChimp_header-invitation-2.png"
          alt="Inauguration"
          width={600}
          height={200}
          style="width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: var(--border-radius-m);"
        />
        <h1>Inauguration et soirée jeux</h1>
        <p><strong>Dimanche 10 juin 2018 à 16h</strong></p>
      </header>

      <section class="flow gap-h4 padding-y-h1">
        <p>
          Il y a de ça un an maintenant, nous sommes partis en quête pour libérer les joueurs de
          leurs entraves. Aujourd'hui, plus que jamais, le mal nous menace mais la rébellion est en
          marche et l'espoir grandit tous les jours dans le cœur des vaillants résistants !
        </p>

        <div class="flow gap-h4 center text">
          <h3>Inscris-toi !</h3>
          <p class="color-red">C'est obligatoire mais gratuit</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Stats -->
      <section class="flow gap-h4 padding-y-h1">
        <ul class="reset grid-fluid" style="--width-column-min: var(--width-col-8);">
          <li
            class="box no-border padding-h4 gap-h4 color-palette-trans background-overlay border-radius-s text-center"
          >
            <p class="h1">+110</p>
            <p>joueurs</p>
          </li>
          <li
            class="box no-border padding-h4 gap-h4 color-palette-trans background-overlay border-radius-s text-center"
          >
            <p class="h1">11</p>
            <p>partenaires</p>
          </li>
          <li
            class="box no-border padding-h4 gap-h4 color-palette-trans background-overlay border-radius-s text-center"
          >
            <p class="h1">+70</p>
            <p>jeux proposés</p>
          </li>
          <li
            class="box no-border padding-h4 gap-h4 color-palette-trans background-overlay border-radius-s text-center"
          >
            <p class="h1">40</p>
            <p>tables créées</p>
          </li>
          <li
            class="box no-border padding-h4 gap-h4 color-palette-trans background-overlay border-radius-s text-center"
          >
            <p class="h1">16</p>
            <p>interviews</p>
          </li>
          <li
            class="box no-border padding-h4 gap-h4 color-palette-trans background-overlay border-radius-s text-center"
          >
            <p class="h1">8</p>
            <p>jeux offerts (Asmodee)</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Règles du jeu -->
      <section class="flow gap-h4 padding-y-h1">
        <h2>Règles du jeu</h2>

        <div class="cluster gap-h1 center text" style="--width-column: 130px;">
          <div class="flow gap-down-h6">
            <img
              src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-02.png"
              alt=""
              style="width: 120px; margin: auto;"
            />
            <p><strong>16h &gt; 22h</strong></p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow gap-down-h6">
            <img
              src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-03.png"
              alt=""
              style="width: 120px; margin: auto;"
            />
            <p><strong>3 &gt; 99 ans</strong></p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow gap-down-h6">
            <img
              src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-04.png"
              alt=""
              style="width: 120px; margin: auto;"
            />
            <p><strong>Coopératif</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- But du jeu -->
      <section class="flow gap-h4 padding-y-h1">
        <h3>But du jeu</h3>
        <p>
          Le temps d'une soirée, nous célébrons <strong>Ruego, le jinn du jeu</strong>. Enchaîne les
          parties de tes jeux préférés pour attirer ses faveurs !
        </p>

        <h3>Déroulement de la "party"</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Accueil des joueurs</strong> • <strong>Explication des règles</strong> •
          <strong>Organisation de tables</strong> • <strong>Et autres surprises…</strong>
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Phases de jeu -->
      <section class="flow gap-h4 padding-y-h1">
        <h3>Phases de jeu</h3>
        <div class="cluster gap-h1 center text">
          <div class="flow gap-h6">
            <img src="/archive/images/WP-MailChimp-invit-02.png" alt="" />
            <p>Un verre au bar</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow gap-h6">
            <img src="/archive/images/WP-MailChimp-invit-03.png" alt="" />
            <p>Grignotages</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow gap-h6">
            <img src="/archive/images/WP-MailChimp-invit-04.png" alt="" />
            <p>Rencontres</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow gap-h6">
            <img src="/archive/images/WP-MailChimp-invit-05.png" alt="" />
            <p>Jeux</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Mise en place -->
      <section class="flow gap-h4 padding-y-h1">
        <h3>Mise en place</h3>
        <div class="flex flow horizontal gap-h1 center text">
          <div class="flow gap-h6">
            <img
              src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-08.png"
              alt=""
              style="width: 100px; margin: auto;"
            />
            <p>Dimanche <strong>10 juin</strong> 2018<br /><strong>16h</strong></p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow gap-h6">
            <img
              src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-09.png"
              alt=""
              style="width: 100px; margin: auto;"
            />
            <p><strong>Espace Maurice Carême</strong><br />rue du Chapelain 1-7, Anderlecht</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Sur place (tilted card) -->
      <section class="flow gap-h4 padding-y-h1">
        <div class="flow gap-h5">
          <h3>Sur place</h3>
          <div class="flex flow horizontal justify-around gap-h4">
            <div class="flow gap-h8">
              <img
                src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-10.png"
                alt=""
                style="width: 100px; margin: auto;"
              />
              <p>Garderie</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flow gap-h8">
              <img
                src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-12.png"
                alt=""
                style="width: 100px; margin: auto;"
              />
              <p>Accessibilité</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flow gap-h8">
              <img
                src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-11.png"
                alt=""
                style="width: 100px; margin: auto;"
              />
              <p>Terrasse</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flow gap-h8">
              <img
                src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-13.png"
                alt=""
                style="width: 100px; margin: auto;"
              />
              <p>WC</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Partenaires -->
      <section class="flow gap-h4 padding-y-h1">
        <div class="center">
          <img src="/archive/images/mailChimp_header-partenaires.png" alt="Partenaires" />
        </div>

        <!-- Partenaires principaux -->
        <div class="flow gap-h4">
          <div>
            <img src="/archive/images/ASMODEE.png" alt="Asmodee" />
            <img src="/archive/images/espace-careme.jpg" alt="Espace Carême" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Autres partenaires -->
        <div class="flow gap-h4">
          <div>
            <img src="/archive/images/Ludivine.png" alt="Ludivine" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/casse-noisettes.png" alt="Casse-Noisettes" />
            <img src="/archive/images/lets-play-together.png" alt="Let's Play Together" />
            <img src="/archive/images/the-cookie-tree.jpg" alt="The Cookie Tree" />
            <img src="/archive/images/jeux-spellen-1082.png" alt="Jeux Spellen" />
            <img src="/archive/images/Geek-Attitude-Games-01.png" alt="GAG" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/jeuxsticiers.png" alt="Jeuxsticiers" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/ace_workshops.png" alt="Ace Workshops" class="partner-logo" />
            <img
              src="/archive/images/ReposProduction.png"
              alt="Repos Production"
              class="partner-logo"
            />
            <img src="/archive/images/de-joueur.png" alt="De Joueur" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/govinda-box.png" alt="Govinda" class="partner-logo" />
            <img
              src="/archive/images/Des-jeux-une-fois.png"
              alt="Des jeux une fois"
              class="partner-logo"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Vidéo -->
      <section class="flow gap-h4 padding-y-h1">
        <h3>Souvenirs en vidéo</h3>
        <iframe
          width="100%"
          height="315"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/laySniWhIU4"
          frameborder="0"
          allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </section>
    </main>
  </BasicPage>
</SkeletonPage>

<style>
  /* Tilted "sur place" card */
  .sur-place-box {
    transform: rotate(-3deg);
    margin: var(--size-h3) auto;
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 600px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-raised-s);
  }

  /* Stat numbers — use color-primary from palette */
  .stat-nb {
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Color helpers not in the global system */
  .color-primary {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  .color-secondary {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }
  .color-red {
    color: var(--color-red);
  }

  /* Partner logos */
  .partner-logo {
    height: 70px;
    width: 70px;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
</style>
